                <expan><abbr>Cl</abbr><ex>audio</ex></expan> Galonio <expan><abbr>an</abbr><ex>norum</ex></expan> XXV scri<lb break="no" n="2"/><expan><abbr>b</abbr><ex>ae</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>Mursel</abbr><ex>lae</ex></expan> hic situs est <lb n="3"/>et Claudio Nigrino <expan><abbr>n<am>n</am></abbr><ex>orum</ex></expan> <lb n="4"/>LXXXV et <expan><abbr>Ulp</abbr><ex>iae</ex></expan> Finitae <expan><abbr>an</abbr><ex>norum</ex></expan> LX <lb n="5"/><expan><abbr>Claud</abbr><ex>ia</ex></expan> Gallonia ob <expan><abbr>memor</abbr><ex>iam</ex></expan> <lb n="6"/>fratris et parentibus vivis <expan><abbr>f</abbr><ex>aciendum</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>c</abbr><ex>uravit</ex></expan>
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Gefunden in Wiederverwendung für ein spätantikes Grab. (B): CIL III: Z. 1: Gallonio; RIU: Z. 6: parentibus f(aciendum) (aber in der Zeichnung richtig).</p>
